Shout random &quot;Push the mob &lt;direction&gt;&quot; instructions and/or phrases like &quot;Watch Push!&quot;  &quot;Into the corner&quot;  &quot;Pin it!&quot;  &quot;I can't believe you just pushed that drake into the lava pit you dumb arse tanks&quot;<br>
